      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next big adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has been really well-loved. It\u2019s perfect for everything from your daily commute to spontaneous weekend road trips. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love it!",
