    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example is paired with a desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with a well-sorted suspension geometry, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. Recent comprehensive service includes a valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the high-revving internal components are within factory tolerances. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with spirited use, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering a linear power band and telepathic steering feedback. This is a mechanically sound specimen ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
